column2: ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. AA SITE IS NEUTRALIZED. SEND IN THE CHOPPERS. OVER.
ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. ROAD IS CLEARED OUT. OVER.
ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. THE FIELD IS SEIZED. NO ENEMIES LEFT. OVER.
THIS IS ALPHA BLACK. HOUDAN IS UNDER NATO CONTROL. ALPHA OUT.
ROGER ALPHA BLACK. GUNSHIPS ON THE WAY. OVER.
COPY THAT ALPHA. WERE SENDING OFFICERS OVER THERE. SECURE HOUDAN FOR THEIR ARRIVAL. OVER.
OFFICERS HAVE ARRIVED TO HOUDAN. GOOD JOB EVERYONE. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. OVER.
